rows.label: tlk41700121_05_msg0001
rows.name:
Superbia and Invidia... When war
finally breaks out between those two,
I'm sure Gula will get mixed up in it.

rows.label: tlk41700121_05_msg0002
rows.name:
But we don't have any fighting forces
of our own. In the end, we're just at the
mercy of whichever side is victorious.

rows.label: tlk41700121_05_msg0003
rows.name:
All we can do is pray that whichever
country wins won't harm our culture
too much.

rows.label: tlk41700121_05_msg0004
rows.name:
Though of course, the best outcome
is if they never go to war to begin with.
